Each tile covers a geographic area 30 mins Latitude x 30 mins Longitude and spans 16 USGS 7.5 minute quadrangles. Some tiles that fall along the state boundary may be comprised of fewer quads.</abstract>    <purpose>The data are created to serve as base information for use in GIS systems for a variety of planning and analysis purposes.
